data.description: Beautiful home in the foothills with Tons of Character! A Perfect location with hiking nearbyIncludes: a remodeled kitchen with granite surfaces, soft close cabinetry slate gray appliance package, slate stone tile flooring in kitchen, new electrical panel and recessed lighting, deck and landscaping in backyard perfect for entertaining and gardening with established perennial plants, a peach and pomegranate trees, and 2 storage sheds. Plenty of room for the dogs with a gated dog run. New Paint, New TPO roof with a 20 yr $600 transferable warranty and a new water heater with a warranty.
